{"tid":2154175,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「如果我做壞事都要做A1」","createTime":"2020-08-13T03:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T04:21:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cd0edaec8787a9a089abdeb82faabaa7be074641","tid":2154175,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T03:42:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/SUGMITCTHHRE6MAZVTNQKNVBOA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FSUGMITCTHHRE6MAZVTNQKNVBOA%2F&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzhUAsmJrpgm%2FsQZzOZZuI0I%3D&h=a46042fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FSUGMITCTHHRE6MAZVTNQKNVBOA%2F&h=49ae9f8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/SUGMITCTHHRE6MAZVTNQKNVBOA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「如果我做壞事都要做A1」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YKSIfsH6wiQsJ14UQIJIwRyO1KA=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CP76ADX4DGQEV5H4CDXN3JSXOE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYKSIfsH6wiQsJ14UQIJIwRyO1KA%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCP76ADX4DGQEV5H4CDXN3JSXOE.jpg&h=8130f1e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎智英、壹傳媒行政總裁張劍虹及營運總裁兼財務總裁周達權昨午在辦公樓層中庭向全體員工講話勉勵大家。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】黎智英昨日與壹傳媒行政總裁、《蘋果日報》社長張劍虹及營運總裁兼財務總裁周達權見員工期間，兩人透露一段逾20年前有關《蘋果日報》編採方針對話。張劍虹稱當年黎智英曾經對他說，若果自己被拉，《蘋果》也要做頭版，黎隨即澄清當時是指「如果我做咗壞事，你哋都要（用嚟）做A1」，今次被捕上《蘋果》頭版並不算。<br />\n<br />\n張劍虹向員工講話時，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n這時黎智英澄清，當時他的意思是「就係如果我做咗壞事，你哋都要（用嚟）做A1」，指今次他上《蘋果》頭版「我唔係做咗壞事，咁做A1係理所當然嘅」，但他繼續表明，若他日後有做壞事「都要（做A1）」。"},{"pid":"705397d3fd629288b110ca4354ba3f4f18ecb5dd","tid":2154175,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:01:29.000Z","msg":"琴晚19話佢似飛越瘋人院的Jack Nicholson<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080ae7719260fb4311c7b390675eed10ba72deeb","tid":2154175,"uid":69231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:07:58.000Z","msg":"好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd5e165be064f2e88af7039d5183451a37eea80","tid":2154175,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:21:44.000Z","msg":"【反守為攻】國際線極缺錢眾籌要你支持！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2149416\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2149416</a>"}]}